author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Bad Omens have released "Specter" - an 'epic' new single and video - so I thought I'd take a look. It was impressive, but I didn't understand. It also led me to speculate about how much could be achieved without all the architecture - so if you've made a music video and you want me to take a look, please send it to me. I'll be reviewing some of them.  The email link is in my home page. 

**For those triggered by long introductions, the review starts at 6'35, which might be a record**

Bad Omens, the full video: https://youtu.be/EUe9UhcUtEI?si=c-wJPokjNevUx3vi
